/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a bustling street scene in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a low angle, giving a sense of the city's towering structures. The buildings lining the street are predominantly red and white, their vibrant colors standing out against the clear blue sky. Chinese characters are visible on some of the buildings, hinting at the cultural richness of the area. The street itself is lined with cars and bicycles, indicating a busy urban environment. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many cities. The image is bathed in the warm glow of a sunny day, casting long shadows and highlighting the architectural details of the buildings.
